{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And the way it was given to us, there was one pot, five people standing, five of them, and one behind the other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "No spoons, no individual dishes, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "One pot and five people had to drink out of that one pot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "The same way we got some unsweetened liquid, that-- brown liquid that was called coffee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Also one pot, five people drinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we got a piece of bread, a square slice that had more sawdust than wheat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But that was the only nutritious part of our-- nutritious part of our diet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Every once in a while we would get a little piece of marmalade or some margarine with our bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And that was also given to us during roll calls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Every once in a while they would give us like a little piece of wurst or some similar kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were two things in Auschwitz, though.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But basically, these roll calls were used for selections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "People who didn't look fit, who didn't look good, which was no big accomplishment under the circumstances, were taken away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And we soon learned that nobody ever came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "There were two things in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I think the most horrible thing was your total sense of isolation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Auschwitz was-- Birkenau, the camps-- totally bare.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "I mean, it was the dirt road, or the cement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Not even a blade of glass-- grass of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "You were totally isolated from the outside world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "At this point, there was nobody between you and your murderers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "There was no reason to shout, because nobody could hear you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And also because of the constant selections there was a sense of hopelessness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "You just did not know one day whether you're going to survive the next day or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
